<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 11:01:22 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Tesla Model 3 及 Model Y 香港加價     2022 一換一新價錢列表</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/telsa311priceup/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=telsa311priceup</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 11:01:22 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[Model 3]]></category><category><![CDATA[Model Y]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tesla]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089655</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>香港 Tesla 旗下 Model 3 及 Model Y 車款將會加價，生效日期為 2022 年 3 月 11 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">香港 Tesla 旗下 Model 3 及 Model Y 車款將會加價，生效日期為 2022 年 3 月 11 日，以下是 1 換 1 新價錢列表。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">Model Y 方面：</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">後驅 (Standard Range) 版將由舊價 HK$ 337, 800 上調 1% 至 HK$ 341, 800；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">長續航 (Long Range) 版將由舊價 HK$ 399, 700 上調 6% 至 HK$ 422, 920；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">Performance 版將由舊價 HK$ 502, 470 上調 3% 至 HK$ 519, 670；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">Model 3 方面：</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">後驅 (Standard Range) 版將由舊價 HK$ 307, 800 上調 3% 至 HK$ 315, 800；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">長續航 (Long Range) 版將由舊價 HK$ 367, 000 上調 3% 至 HK$ 377, 800；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">Performance 版將由舊價 HK$ 459, 470 上調 4% 至 HK$ 476, 670。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">在眾車款中，以 Tesla Model Y Long Range 版加幅最大，達到 6%；而 Model Y 的 Standard Range 版本加幅 1% 為最少。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">另外，Tesla 的顏色選項亦有價格調整：珍珠白 (多塗層) 將在 3 月 11 號後由免費調整為 HK$ 9, 600；純黑則由 HK$ 9,600 調整為免費；另外夜銀、深藍則維持原價 HK$9,600；亮紅 (多塗層) 亦沒有變動，維持於 HK$ 12,800。</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n-694x406.png" alt="" width="694" height="406" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n-694x406.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n-1280x748.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n-768x449.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n-1536x897.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/275284590_10166460326920495_1661533099657502809_n.png 1554w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料及圖片來源：Tesla</p><p><span style="font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></span></p></p><div class="feedflare">
