</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>俄羅斯重開盜版網站 RuTracker     收藏破解版軟件及電影</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/rutracker/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=rutracker</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 06:48:45 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089560</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>俄羅斯因入侵烏克蘭戰事被不少社交、串流平台，以及軟件廠商等企業宣佈停止提供服務，當局為應對局面，宣布重開俄羅斯 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>俄羅斯因入侵烏克蘭戰事被不少社交、串流平台，以及軟件廠商等企業宣佈停止提供服務，當局為應對局面，宣布重開俄羅斯最大的盜版資源網站 RuTracker.org，該網站曾於 2015 年遭通信監管機構 Roskomnadzor 封鎖。</p><p>俄羅斯受局勢影響，Microsoft、Adobe、Xbox、CD Projekt、Netflix、Meta 等軟件廠商、知名遊戲公司、社交以及串流平台紛紛紛宣布不再支持於俄羅斯地區服務，導致當地民眾的娛樂大受影響。相信俄羅斯為避免當地民眾的娛樂因戰事受制裁影響而感到不滿，因此重啟 2015 為打擊盜版而關閉資源網站 RuTracker.org。用戶可以在該網站下載 Windows、Microsoft Office、AutoCAD 等破解版軟件，以及荷里活電影和電視節目。</p><p>有不少外國網友曾嘗試登入網站，但目前只有俄羅斯的 IP 地址才能連接。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://gamingsym.in/rutracker-org-once-the-largest-resource-website-in-russia-has-recently-been-unblocked-after-microsoft-adobe-game-developers-etc-announced-that-they-are-banned-from-selling-products-in-russia/">gamingsym</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=wg1T57MPdBw:k-8BNVHMsNU:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=wg1T57MPdBw:k-8BNVHMsNU:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>《Elden Ring》Steam 近百萬人同時玩，成榜上歷史紀錄第 6 位</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/eldenring/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=eldenring</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 06:43:05 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Elden Ring]]></category><category><![CDATA[PC 遊戲]]></category><category><![CDATA[steam]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089523</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>由 FromSoft Studio 製作、高崎英高監製、名小說家喬治·R·R·馬丁編劇的 《Elden Ring [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>由 FromSoft Studio 製作、高崎英高監製、名小說家喬治·R·R·馬丁編劇的 《Elden Ring》自 2 月 25 日在三平台推出後，熱潮居高不下。新作在結合此前同類魂系遊戲如《 Dark Souls 》三部曲與《隻狼》的特點之外，更融合開放世界與騎馬戰等特色。</p><p>據統計平台 Steam DB 資料，近一週內《Elden Ring》在 Steam 平台的玩家同時在線人數不斷上升，由 3 月 1 日的六十三萬在一週內穩定增加，直至 3 月 6 日時登頂，高峰達 953, 426 人， 在串流平台 Twitch 上亦引來近五十萬人觀看遊戲直播。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-2-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-2-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-2-768x453.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-2.jpg 964w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這項紀錄令 《Elden Ring》 成為單機遊戲類別中登頂，同時亦超越此前 《Monster Hunter: World》的近 33 萬人同時在線紀錄，成為日製遊戲的新高峰；此外，《Elden Ring》 亦成為榜上歷史紀錄的第六位，位列 CyberPunk 2077 之下。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER-768x422.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ER.jpg 1248w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>作品更獲眾多遊戲評論媒體的高度讚譽，在 Metacritic 獲得三平台逾 95 分的一致好評。即使早前曾有網民投訴 PC 版的畫質優化未完善，經常出現掉幀及畫面卡頓的情況，但仍無阻熱潮，現時遊戲仍有超過 60 萬人在線，Steam 上亦獲得 84% 的玩家極度好評。相信叫好又叫座的《Eldeng Ring》仍有機會創造更高紀錄。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://steamdb.info/app/1245620/graphs/">Steam DB</a></p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=N3hdi2AqXC8:W2FZ5HGUB28:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=N3hdi2AqXC8:W2FZ5HGUB28:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>俄羅斯或中斷全球互聯網連接，政府網站率先脫網防入侵</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/russia-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=russia-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 06:17:55 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089532</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日前有傳俄羅斯因入侵烏克蘭的關係，遭到各國家、黑客、科技及社交媒體等組織的抵制和入侵，導致考慮準備啟動其可以獨 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日前有傳俄羅斯因入侵烏克蘭的關係，遭到各國家、黑客、科技及社交媒體等組織的抵制和入侵，導致考慮準備啟動其可以獨立運行的國內網際網路 Runet，斷開國內網絡用戶和全球互聯網的連接。俄羅斯聯邦通信、信息技術和大眾傳媒監督局否認傳聞。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Russia?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Russia</a> began active preparations for disconnection from the global Internet</p><p>No later than March 11, all servers and domains must be transferred to the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Russian?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Russian</a> zone. In addition, detailed data on the network infrastructure of the sites is being collected. <a href="https://t.co/wOCdRqOJej">pic.twitter.com/wOCdRqOJej</a></p><p>&mdash; NEXTA (@nexta_tv) <a href="https://twitter.com/nexta_tv/status/1500553480548892679?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 6, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>該部門發表一份報告表示，雖然針對俄羅斯網站的網絡攻擊不斷發生，但已做好了各種準備來保障俄羅斯網絡資源的使用，並且已向當地政府部門和公司提供簡單的網絡安全建議，以保護資源免受惡意入侵、保持服務運行，暫時沒有斷開與國際互聯網連接的打算。</p><p>該報告補充指，俄羅斯政府仍對作出抵制行動的公司和國持開放態度，相信此聲明的主要目的是為了規避更多的外部制裁。</p><p>俄羅斯的互聯網遭受到許多國際企業中止服務，例如美國跨國網際網路服務供應商 Cogent Communications 部分切斷了向俄羅斯客戶的服務，減慢俄羅斯用戶訪問網站的速度。但有許多倡導互聯網自由和獨立者反對西方國家公司對俄羅斯進行的網絡制裁，認為做法會阻止當地民眾接收真實資訊。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.financemagnates.com/fintech/news/is-russia-disconnecting-from-the-global-internet/">financemagnates</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=0qFJOqL8vfo:2evn2GY0LwI:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=0qFJOqL8vfo:2evn2GY0LwI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Steam 俄羅斯無法使用電子支付，用戶無法購買任何遊戲</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/russiasteam/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=russiasteam</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[samuel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 06:06:47 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[電子支付]]></category><category><![CDATA[steam]]></category><category><![CDATA[俄羅斯]]></category><category><![CDATA[信用卡]]></category><category><![CDATA[網上支付平台]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089561</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>自烏俄戰爭爆發，陸續有國際企業對俄羅斯作出制裁，包括多間網絡支付平台與信用卡公司，此舉引來連鎖效應，令俄羅斯地 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>自烏俄戰爭爆發，陸續有國際企業對俄羅斯作出制裁，包括多間網絡支付平台與信用卡公司，此舉引來連鎖效應，令俄羅斯地區用戶無法在 Steam 平台上購物。</p><p>非官方 Twitter 賬號 Steam Status ( Unofficial ) 在上週發文，指俄羅斯用戶無法再用信用卡在平台上購物。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Users in Russia may not be able to purchase games on Steam due to credit card purchases failing.</p><p>&mdash; Steam Status (Unofficial) (@SteamStatus) <a href="https://twitter.com/SteamStatus/status/1499041708037836809?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 2, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>雖然 Steam 一直未有宣佈加入制裁俄羅斯，但因先前<a href="https://unwire.hk/2022/03/03/paypal-3/hottopic/spotlight/">報道</a>的 Paypal、Visa 與 Mastercard 等多個支付平台的聯手行動而受到影響。而經小編查證後，發現在俄羅斯地區 Steam 平台界面上，用戶仍可將遊戲加入購物車，但付款界面上的所有支付方式都會顯示為無法使用。令俄版 Steam 變相停止服務。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-1089562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/steam-1.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="352" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089563" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/steam-2-694x286.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="286" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/steam-2-694x286.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/steam-2-768x316.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/steam-2.jpg 961w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/SteamStatus/status/1499041708037836809">Twitter</a>、Steam</p><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=pddhF829MwQ:wBrytn_6iqE:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=pddhF829MwQ:wBrytn_6iqE:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Lenovo MWC 2022 新品巡禮　ThinkPad 首用 ARM 架構　抵玩入門白電競筆電</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/lenovo-mwc-2022-intro/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=lenovo-mwc-2022-intro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 05:59:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[gaming]]></category><category><![CDATA[Ideapad]]></category><category><![CDATA[lenovo]]></category><category><![CDATA[ThinkBook]]></category><category><![CDATA[ThinkPad]]></category><category><![CDATA[ThinkVision]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089572</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>每年的 MWC，一眾廠商都會相繼推出上半年的重點新機，Lenovo 亦不例外，繼 CES 後，在今年的 MWC [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>每年的 MWC，一眾廠商都會相繼推出上半年的重點新機，Lenovo 亦不例外，繼 CES 後，在今年的 MWC 亦推出了一系列的新機，當中最吸引的也有數部，現在就為大家分享一下吧。</p><h2>ThinkPad X13s Gen 1：首採 ARM 架構 ThinkPad</h2><p>今次 Lenovo 推出多部新機，當中最值得留意的，肯定是 ThinkPad 旗下首部採用 ARM 架構處理器的手提電腦 X13s Gen 1。它是世上首部採用 Qualcomm Snapdraon 8cx Gen 3 這枚 64-bit ARM 架構 5nm 制程處理器的手提電腦，而且是首部 ThinkPad 支援 5G mmWave 技術（雖然香港未用到），方便用家隨時隨地都可以連接網絡工作，加上機身採用用輕薄設計，機身厚度只有 13mm，重量亦只有 1.06kg，十分適合需要經常外攜及隨時上網工作的商務用家使用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-1280x723.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-768x434.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-1536x867.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-2048x1156.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089577" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-1280x719.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-2048x1151.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-1280x723.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-768x434.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-1536x868.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-2048x1157.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於其他規格，包括：內建了最高 32GB LPDDR4x 記憶體、最多 1TB PCIe SSD、13.3 吋 16：10 長闊比 1920 x 1200 解像度 IPS 熒幕及 500 萬像素 RGB 前鏡頭。Lenovo 表示將會在今年五月推出 ThinkPad X13s Gen 1，定價為 1,399 歐羅（約 HK$11,905）起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-615x580.jpg" alt="" width="615" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-615x580.jpg 615w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-955x900.jpg 955w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-768x724.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001.jpg 1528w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 615px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089580" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-614x580.jpg" alt="" width="614" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-614x580.jpg 614w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-953x900.jpg 953w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-768x725.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002.jpg 1525w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 614px" /></a></p><h2>IdeaPad Gaming 3 / 3i：入門版迷人白電競機</h2><p>去到今時今日，已不是喜歡打機的用家才會入手電競款手提電腦，一些家居環境較細，又想擁有一部具備一定效能電腦的用家，也會對入門級的電競機款有興趣。Lenovo 在今次的 MWC 就發佈了入門級的電競筆電 IdeaPad Gaming 3 / 3i（3 為 AMD 版本，3i 為 Intel 版本），設有 15 吋及 16 吋熒幕款式供用家選擇，當中尤以 15 吋機款最為吸引，因為它有白色機款，即使女性用家亦十分適合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089581" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>機身設計上十分具時尚感，而且配備了最新的 Intel Core 或 AMD Ryzen 處理器，獨顯最高更可配置 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060，加上十分足夠的端子，是 Desktop Replacement 的最佳選擇之一。熒幕方面，不但具備 2560 x 1440 解像度，而且更支援最高 165Hz 更新率，即使用來打機畫面亦十分流暢。此外，它亦內建了四散熱風扇設計，打機時可以有效將機內熱力帶出機外，令系統長保穩定。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089585" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>至於推出日期方面，IdeaPad Gaming 3 / 3i 的 15 吋版本，將會分別在今年的六月及五月推出，定價均為 999 歐羅（約 HK$8,503）起；至於 Gaming 3 / 3i 的 16 吋版本，則會分別在今年的七月及六月正式推出，定價均為 1,099 歐羅（約 HK$9,360）起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089584" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2>ThinkBook 13x Gen 4 i / 14s Yoga Gen 2：設計更輕更硬淨</h2><p>另一個今年 Lenovo 新推出的機款系列就是 ThinkBook，在今次 MWC 他們推出了傳統筆電設計商務機款 ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i，以及擁有可旋轉式觸控熒幕，可作筆電可作平板二用的 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2。兩部機均採用了近年 ThinkBook 沿用的兩截深淺色機身設計，今代更採用了全金屬機身，更加硬淨之餘看上去亦更有型。另外，兩部機的機身相比上代都輕薄了，ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i 厚度及重量只有 14.9mm 及 1.26kg，而 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2 亦分別只有 16.9mm 及 1.5kg，外攜使用亦十分方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089587" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>熒幕方面，ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i 採用了 13.3 吋 2.5K 幼邊框熒幕，而 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2 就採用了 14 吋 1080p 幼邊框觸控熒幕，兩部機預設設定分別只是後者支援觸控功能而前者就不支援。另外作為輕薄機款，兩部機除了都擁有 2 個支援 Thunderbolt 4 的 USB-C 插槽外，亦設有傳統的 USB-A 插槽，接駁周邊十分方便。規格方面，兩部機均內建了最新第 12 代 Intel Core i7 處理器、最高 32GB（13s）/ 40GB（14s Yoga）記憶體、Intel Iris Xe 圖像處理晶片等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089588" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>至於推出日期方面，兩部機均會在今年六月推出發售，定價方面，ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i 為 749 歐羅（約 HK$6,366）起，而 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2 則為 899 歐羅（約 HK$7,641）起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1089590 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089591" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1089592 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2>ThinkVision M14d：解像度更高設計未變</h2><p>近年不少人都需要 WFH，如果想提升工作效率，使用雙熒幕或許也是個好選擇。今次筆者最後一項覺得值得為大家介紹的，就是 Lenovo 今次發佈的升級版便攜式外置顯示器 ThinkVision M14d。在外型上它與前代分別不大，功能上亦未有大變，不過今代熒幕解像度就提升至 2240 x 1400 2.2K，更高的解像度可說是針對近年開始 2K 解像度 16：10 長闊比熒幕變主流的商務筆電而設。當然，針對仍然在用 16：9 長闊比熒幕的用家，它亦設有按鍵可以轉換長闊比，十分體貼。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>至於推出日期方面，ThinkVision M14d 將會在今年八月正式推出，定價方面為 359 歐羅（約 HK$3,051）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089597" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
